<h3 id="sec:req:gen.ops">4.1.2 GEN.OPS – Device Operation<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:gen.ops" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<table>
<col width="20%" />
<col width="80%" />
<tr class="header">
