<h4 id="sec:req:wan.dhcpc.bfdecho">4.2.5.2 WAN.DHCPC.BFDecho – BFD echo<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:wan.dhcpc.bfdecho" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

