<td align="left"><span id="req:wan.dhcpc.bfdecho.1">WAN.DHCPC.BFDecho.1<a class="headerlink" href="#req:wan.dhcpc.bfdecho.1" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
