<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:wan.trans.v4-release-control.3">WAN.TRANS.v4-release-control.3<a class="headerlink" href="#req:wan.trans.v4-release-control.3" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST provide signaling to the BNG according to RFC 1332 <span class="cite" data-citation-ids="RFC1332"><a href='#ref-RFC1332' title=''>[53]</a></span>.</td>
