<h4 id="sec:req:lan.fw.spi">4.3.15.1 LAN.FW.SPI – Firewall (Advanced)<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:lan.fw.spi" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

