<td align="left"><span id="req:lan.filter.content.1">LAN.FILTER.CONTENT.1<a class="headerlink" href="#req:lan.filter.content.1" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MAY support filtering based on web content or URL string
screening techniques on a per LAN device basis.</td>
</tr>
