<h3 id="sec:req:lan.diagnostics">4.3.17 LAN.DIAGNOSTICS – Automated User Diagnostics<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:lan.diagnostics" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

