<h3 id="sec:req:mgmt.remote">4.4.4 MGMT.REMOTE – Remote Management<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:mgmt.remote" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<h4 id="sec:req:mgmt.remote.tr-069">4.4.4.1 MGMT.REMOTE.TR-069 – Remote Management (TR-069)<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:mgmt.remote.tr-069" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

<table>
<col width="20%" />
<col width="80%" />
<tr class="header">
<th align="left">ID</th>
<th align="left">Requirement</th>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:mgmt.remote.tr-069.1">MGMT.REMOTE.TR-069.1<a class="headerlink" href="#req:mgmt.remote.tr-069.1" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST support the remote management protocol as defined in
