<h4 id="sec:req:if.wan.xdsl">4.5.1.3 IF.WAN.xDSL – xDSL General Requirements<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:if.wan.xdsl" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

<table>
<col width="20%" />
<col width="80%" />
<tr class="header">
<th align="left">ID</th>
<th align="left">Requirement</th>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:if.wan.xdsl.1">IF.WAN.xDSL.1<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.wan.xdsl.1" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
