</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:if.wan.xdsl.5">IF.WAN.xDSL.5<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.wan.xdsl.5" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST only synchronize within the minimum and maximum line rate
