</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td align="left"><span id="req:if.wan.xdsl.6">IF.WAN.xDSL.6<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.wan.xdsl.6" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">RG packet forwarding performance and throughput MUST keep up with the
DSL line rate.</td>
</tr>
</table>

