<h3 id="sec:req:if.lan">4.5.2 IF.LAN – LAN Interface Modules<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:if.lan" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<h4 id="sec:req:if.lan.eth">4.5.2.1 IF.LAN.ETH – Ethernet (LAN)<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:if.lan.eth" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

<table>
<col width="20%" />
<col width="80%" />
<tr class="header">
<th align="left">ID</th>
<th align="left">Requirement</th>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:if.lan.eth.1">IF.LAN.ETH.1<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.lan.eth.1" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST support use of a straight-through (patch) cable between the
Ethernet interface and a PC.</td>
</tr>
<tr class="even">
<td align="left"><span id="req:if.lan.eth.2">IF.LAN.ETH.2<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.lan.eth.2" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
