<h4 id="sec:req:if.lan.homepna">4.5.2.5 IF.LAN.HomePNA – HomePNA (Phoneline/Coax<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:if.lan.homepna" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

