<td align="left"><span id="req:if.lan.homepna.17">IF.LAN.HomePNA.17<a class="headerlink" href="#req:if.lan.homepna.17" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
