user interface(s).</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:sec.userinterface.5">SEC.USERINTERFACE.5<a class="headerlink" href="#req:sec.userinterface.5" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
