<tr class="even">
<td align="left"><span id="req:sec.userinterface.6">SEC.USERINTERFACE.6<a class="headerlink" href="#req:sec.userinterface.6" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST use exponential rate limiting of login attempts upon failed
login attempts.</td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:sec.userinterface.7">SEC.USERINTERFACE.7<a class="headerlink" href="#req:sec.userinterface.7" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
