<h2 class="new-file new-page" id="sec:req:rgsmart">4.7 RGSMART – Smart Residential Gateway<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:rgsmart" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h2>

