<h4 id="sec:req:rgsmart.oplat.ee">4.7.1.2 RGSMART.OPLAT.EE – Execution Environment<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:rgsmart.oplat.ee" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

