<h4 id="sec:req:regional.na.led">4.8.1.2 REGIONAL.NA.LED – North American LED Indicators<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:regional.na.led" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h4>

