<td align="left"><p><span id="req:regional.na.led.9">REGIONAL.NA.LED.9<a class="headerlink" href="#req:regional.na.led.9" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></p></td>
