<h2 class="new-file new-page" id="sec:req:5g-wwc">4.9 5G-WWC – General 5G WWC<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:req:5g-wwc" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h2>

