<tr class="even">
<td align="left"><span id="req:5g-wwc.wan.up.2">5G-WWC.WAN.UP.2<a class="headerlink" href="#req:5g-wwc.wan.up.2" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The RG MUST support the IPv4, IPv6, IPv4/v6 and Ethernet PDU session
types.</td>
