<h3 class="appendix3" id="sec:local-management">IV.2.1 Local Management<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:local-management" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<ul>
<li>The RG may allow access to a local management interface via a
default address (described in section LAN.ADDRESS).</li>
