<h2 class="appendix2" id="sec:unmanaged-bridge">IV.3 Unmanaged Bridge<a class="headerlink" href="#sec:unmanaged-bridge" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h2>

<ul>
<li><p>The RG does not establish any layer 3 connectivity to the WAN.</p></li>
<li><p>All DHCP requests from the PCs are bridged to the WAN (described in
section WAN.BRIDGE).</p></li>
